    <item>
      <title>法官威胁特朗普因违反禁言令而入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监督唐纳德·特朗普封口费审判的纽约法官表示，如果这位前总统继续违反旨在保护陪审员和证人安全的禁言令，他可能别无选择，只能入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多风暴袭击休斯顿地区，数百人从洪水中获救</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿（美联社）——在 2024 年 5 月 5 日发表的一篇关于德克萨斯州洪水的报道中，美联社依赖当地官员，错误地报道了约翰逊县一名被洪水卷走后死亡的儿童的年龄。这名儿童的年龄是 4 岁，而不是 5 岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 04:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
